289
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,120
I just wanted to go for this look.

290
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:32,200
Isn't it cool?

291
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:33,919
Cool.

292
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,200
I'm off then.

293
00:11:35,919 --> 00:11:36,480
