298
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:48,679
Out of sight, out of mind.

299
00:11:50,919 --> 00:11:51,440
Chairman Fang.

300
00:11:53,279 --> 00:11:55,480
About the Nanshang TV Spring Festival Gala...

301
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,919
we still need to trouble you.

302
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:59,519
To find a small segment for our Xiao Tian.

303
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,200
Just to show his face.

304
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,080
Singing or dancing.

305
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:05,039
Sir, I can perform a skit.

306
00:12:05,799 --> 00:12:07,480
And promote my hometown's potatoes.

307
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:09,120
The dry matter content is very high... No, no, no.

308
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:09,639
Alright, alright.

309
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:12,399
Singing works.

310
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:13,840
He sings better than he speaks, right, brother?

311
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:14,840
If he goes off-key...

312
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:15,840
