313
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,039
Add some autotune or something.

314
00:12:17,519 --> 00:12:18,320
Dancing is no problem either.

315
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:19,960
This kid has great stamina.

316
00:12:20,799 --> 00:12:21,519
And my potatoes...

317
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,519
Okay, okay, okay.

318
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:24,080
No, no, stop with the potatoes.

319
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,120
This... this kid.

320
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:26,879
Fine.

321
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,080
We can arrange a duet.

322
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:31,759
Our company has a girl to promote right now.

323
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:34,720
Later, they could co-star in a mini web series.

324
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:35,960
Hype them up as a couple or something.

325
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:37,519
That's wonderful.

326
00:12:37,919 --> 00:12:38,279
Brother.

327
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,639
As his manager...

328
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:40,960
regarding his...

329
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,399
career path planning...

330
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,600
I'm also considering whether to...

331
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,679
steer him down the acting path.

332
00:12:45,679 --> 00:12:46,039
Right?

333
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:46,639
Yes, yes, yes.

334
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:49,159
Has your kid studied acting?

335
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,120
I've trained him.

336
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:54,879
Brother, has your kid studied acting?

337
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:56,799
Does acting need to be learned?

338
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,240
No need. Just knowing how to speak is enough.

339
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,000
Can you speak?

340
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:04,600
I... I guess so.

341
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:06,240
It's a deal.

342
00:13:07,519 --> 00:13:08,000
Brother.

343
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,039
Come on, let's us two brothers...

344
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:12,559
have a good catch-up, shall we?

345
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:16,720
Brother Maizi

346
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,039
I need to take this call.

347
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,000
Okay, go ahead, go ahead, go ahead.

348
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:23,840
Hello, Guifang.

349
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,240
Can you talk right now?

350
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,120
Yes, go ahead.

351
00:13:27,159 --> 00:13:28,559
Do you have plans for the holidays?

352
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:30,240
Holidays?

353
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:33,039
What the heck is this?

354
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:36,679
The kid's mind is just full of potatoes right now.

355
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,080
I don't know what else to say about him.

356
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:39,639
You...

357
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,039
You're different. You're potato chips.

358
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,399
Bro, is there anything else?

359
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:47,519
I don't have plans for this holiday.

360
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,799
Like that movie...

361
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:51,159
Going to Hainan for fun.

362
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:52,399
Sure!

363
00:13:53,039 --> 00:13:54,960
I, Li Wai, was born for sun and sand.

364
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,399
Don't get too excited yet.

365
00:13:57,759 --> 00:13:59,240
My mom wants us to help count bugs.

366
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,240
That's fine.

367
00:14:01,159 --> 00:14:02,200
No, bro, there aren't many people here.

368
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:02,919
Where are you?

369
00:14:02,919 --> 00:14:03,559
I don't see you.

370
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,679
I'm right here.

371
00:14:04,799 --> 00:14:05,440
Where are you?

372
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,279
I'm raising my hand.

373
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:09,279
There's a popcorn head in front of me.

374
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:10,200
The kind with curls.

375
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,039
Do you see me?

376
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:14,639
It's Reggae style.

377
00:14:18,039 --> 00:14:18,360
Me.

378
00:14:18,919 --> 00:14:19,799
Oh my god.

379
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,320
No...

380
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,000
Bro...

381
00:14:22,399 --> 00:14:23,320
How did you... You, you, you...

382
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,600
Why did you get this hairstyle?

383
00:14:24,679 --> 00:14:25,519
It's definitely shocking.

384
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,120
Fashion. Retro.

385
00:14:27,279 --> 00:14:28,639
This look of yours has exceeded...

386
00:14:28,639 --> 00:14:30,320
...the scope of my understanding of fashion.

387
00:14:32,039 --> 00:14:32,600
Xu Rui!

388
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:33,799
Xu Rui!

389
00:14:34,279 --> 00:14:34,759
Xu Rui!

390
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:35,799
Xu Rui!

391
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:37,440
Xu Rui!

392
00:14:42,039 --> 00:14:43,360
Go, Sister Rui!

393
00:14:43,519 --> 00:14:44,759
Number One Long Legs!

394
00:14:44,919 --> 00:14:46,159
Sister Rui, Sister Rui!

395
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,360
Come on, Xu Rui!

396
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:48,399
Your attention seeker.

397
00:14:48,399 --> 00:14:48,919
Come on!

398
00:14:48,919 --> 00:14:50,360
Go, Xu Rui!

399
00:14:50,559 --> 00:14:51,919
I just like how he stands out.

400
00:14:52,159 --> 00:14:53,320
Xu Rui, Xu Rui!

401
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,679
You stand out even more.

402
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,360
Look at this PDA.

403
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,600
Go, Xu Rui!

404
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:58,759
Number One Long Legs. Come here, let me say a few words.

405
00:14:58,759 --> 00:14:59,480
Quiet, quiet, quiet.

406
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,279
Listen to me for a moment.

407
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:00,879
Students.

408
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,360
Today is our...

409
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:04,240
...last training session before the competition.

410
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:07,279
I hope everyone can seize this window of opportunity...

411
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,240
...to ramp up the intensity.

412
00:15:08,559 --> 00:15:09,960
So that during the competition...

413
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,360
...we can get a good result.

414
00:15:11,559 --> 00:15:12,159
Do you have confidence?

415
00:15:12,399 --> 00:15:13,240
Yes!

416
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:14,440
Let's go! Let's go!

417
00:15:14,519 --> 00:15:15,639
Stretch out, stretch out.

418
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,120
Xu Rui

419
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:24,600
Sister Rui

420
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,200
Come on

421
00:15:25,519 --> 00:15:26,159
Come on

422
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:28,159
Come on

423
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:29,960
Come on

424
00:15:30,159 --> 00:15:31,559
Come on

425
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,759
Come on, Kong Xiaocan

426
00:15:33,759 --> 00:15:35,759
Why can you still smile so brightly?

427
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,320
Like nothing happened.

428
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:38,679
So your mom becoming like this...

429
00:15:38,679 --> 00:15:39,519
...is all because of you, isn't it?

430
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:40,919
This thing... it's a bit complicated.

431
00:15:40,919 --> 00:15:42,039
So you're dying soon, right?

432
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,519
It's possible.

433
00:15:44,919 --> 00:15:45,480
Time to run.

434
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:48,519
Everyone ready?

435
00:15:49,679 --> 00:15:51,399
On your marks.

436
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:55,120
I traded fifty years of life energy for my mom.

437
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:55,720
This matter...

438
00:15:55,919 --> 00:15:56,799
...if anyone finds out...

439
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:57,879
...there will be a punishment.

440
00:15:57,879 --> 00:16:00,639
A very, very severe punishment.

441
00:16:01,039 --> 00:16:02,720
Just forget everything I just said.

442
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,639
I... I hope you'll be happy.

443
00:16:04,919 --> 00:16:06,240
But there are things I can't explain. Fine.

444
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,360
It's a bit complicated. Anyway, it has nothing to do with me anymore.

445
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,559
You know how much I like you.

446
00:16:08,559 --> 00:16:09,279
I have no choice.

447
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:10,519
I'm sorry.

448
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,000
So...

449
00:16:12,639 --> 00:16:14,759
...this is the secret you couldn't tell me.

450
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:17,559
The secret you've been carrying alone for so long.

451
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,039
Xu Rui.

452
00:16:26,639 --> 00:16:27,279
What happened?

453
00:16:27,279 --> 00:16:27,799
Are you okay?

454
00:16:38,519 --> 00:16:39,679
I thought it was all healed.

455
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,200
This is on me too.

456
00:16:43,159 --> 00:16:45,080
I knew you still had issues with that jerk...

457
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,480
...yet I still increased your training intensity.

458
00:16:46,799 --> 00:16:48,639
I only considered that your body could take it.

459
00:16:49,159 --> 00:16:50,440
I didn't consider your state of mind.

460
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,120
My mistake.

461
00:16:53,679 --> 00:16:54,720
Don't blame yourself, Coach.

462
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:57,159
It's my fault for not adjusting my state properly.

463
00:16:57,159 --> 00:16:57,559
Say no more.

464
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,080
I'll go reflect on it.

465
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:04,680
Dear.

466
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:06,960
What are you doing here?

467
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:08,960
Do you want to consider...

468
00:17:09,039 --> 00:17:10,640
...the trade to cure your ankle?

469
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:12,119
Last time I told you six years.

470
00:17:12,319 --> 00:17:14,119
Now I'm offering a huge discount.

471
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:15,400
Five years and eleven months.

472
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,720
I told you already.

473
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,400
I'm not interested in your stuff.

474
00:17:18,519 --> 00:17:19,559
I don't know if others would trade.

475
00:17:19,559 --> 00:17:20,519
But I won't.

476
00:17:20,519 --> 00:17:21,200
That's cheating.

477
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,720
Then all those people outside...

478
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,559
...they are all your fellow athletes.

479
00:17:25,799 --> 00:17:26,960
Do any of them need a trade?

480
00:17:27,039 --> 00:17:29,039
You want me to help you drum up business, right?

481
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:31,920
Then I'll go myself.

482
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:36,759
Let me ask you.

483
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,759
You took fifty years from Xiaocan.

484
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:41,480
What will the result be?

485
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:45,119
The result is Xiaocan lives fifty years less.

486
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:48,759
Then...

487
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:53,400
...when will he die?

488
00:17:54,079 --> 00:17:54,720
How will he die?

489
00:17:55,119 --> 00:17:56,079
Can you tell me?

490
00:17:57,319 --> 00:17:57,759
Dear.

491
00:17:58,880 --> 00:17:59,640
I am very sorry.

492
00:17:59,799 --> 00:18:01,680
I cannot comment.

493
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,440
Business calls.

494
00:18:08,359 --> 00:18:08,880
I'll take my leave.

495
00:18:23,519 --> 00:18:24,519
Are you okay, Xu Rui?

496
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:25,599
I'm fine. Just a scratch.

497
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:26,319
You guys carry on.

498
00:18:26,599 --> 00:18:27,240
Are you sure?

499
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,039
I'm sure. I'm off.

500
00:18:28,039 --> 00:18:28,680
Take it easy then.

501
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:29,039
It's fine.

502
00:18:31,359 --> 00:18:31,880
Xu Rui.

503
00:18:32,799 --> 00:18:33,319
Xu Rui.

504
00:18:35,359 --> 00:18:35,880
How is it?

505
00:18:36,359 --> 00:18:38,039
Does it hurt now? Is it swollen?

506
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,799
Did they spray that medicine on you just now?

507
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,759
Can... can you still walk?

508
00:18:41,799 --> 00:18:42,279
Are you okay?

509
00:18:43,119 --> 00:18:44,200
Slow down. Slow down, slow down.

510
00:18:44,839 --> 00:18:46,160
What did they wrap this with?

511
00:18:46,680 --> 00:18:47,519
It doesn't look swollen.

512
00:18:48,279 --> 00:18:49,720
Do you want to go to the hospital to check again?

513
00:18:50,839 --> 00:18:51,680
Does... does it really not hurt?

514
00:18:52,319 --> 00:18:53,640
Are... are you unhappy?

515
00:18:57,799 --> 00:18:58,960
Don't... don't be unhappy.

516
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,640
Bumps and bruises are normal.

517
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,039
If... if you're really worried...

518
00:19:03,039 --> 00:19:04,240
Maybe we should still go to the hospital.

519
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:06,440
It's fine.

520
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:08,799
Come with me somewhere.

521
00:19:10,079 --> 00:19:11,319
Hurry up.

522
00:19:11,319 --> 00:19:12,559
Wait, is this necessary?

523
00:19:12,559 --> 00:19:13,440
Taking photos too?

524
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,839
It took a lot of effort to get this look.

525
00:19:14,839 --> 00:19:15,720
It's embarrassing. Hurry up.

526
00:19:16,359 --> 00:19:17,720
So embarrassing. I've been styled like this.

527
00:19:19,119 --> 00:19:19,640
Come on, come on.

528
00:19:19,759 --> 00:19:20,480
Look forward. Look forward.

529
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:22,640
Look happier.

530
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:24,039
Smile.

531
00:20:12,799 --> 00:20:13,319
I'm done.

532
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:19,359
No, no, no.

533
00:20:19,359 --> 00:20:20,759
What are you doing? I... I can't...

534
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:22,759
What? You still have an idol image?

535
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:24,440
I've always been in this lane.

536
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:25,400
It'll look so ugly if I take it off.

537
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:25,880
Don't move.

538
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:26,759
No, you...

539
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:29,039
Is... is your foot okay?

540
00:20:29,119 --> 00:20:29,839
Do you want to go check it?

541
00:20:29,839 --> 00:20:30,400
It's fine now.

542
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:31,559
I can even jump.

543
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:32,440
Really, I'm fine.

544
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:33,720
Don't move.

545
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:34,519
No, no.

546
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:36,519
This... this...

547
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,160
It's so ugly.

548
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,759
This... of course it's so ugly.

549
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:41,079
No way.

550
00:20:41,079 --> 00:20:42,160
I feel like I'm naked.

551
00:20:42,839 --> 00:20:44,240
Can't I just draw them on for you?

552
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,240
Let go.

553
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:57,440
Don't move.

554
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,400
This looks much better.

555
00:21:30,759 --> 00:21:32,680
A Fu's punishment is really strange.

556
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:34,920
If it weren't for the hair and eyebrows falling out together...

557
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:39,000
For girls, this would be painless permanent hair removal.

558
00:21:39,319 --> 00:21:40,640
They'd wake up laughing from their dreams.

559
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:44,759
Xu Rui, I shouldn't have dragged you into this.

560
00:21:47,559 --> 00:21:49,559
I'm actually quite happy.

561
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,720
I finally know

562
00:21:52,279 --> 00:21:53,559
why you broke up with me.

563
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:55,720
Why you wouldn't get back together.

564
00:21:56,519 --> 00:21:59,079
I finally understand your predicament.

565
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:01,240
I'm sorry.

566
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:02,519
No need to apologize.

567
00:22:04,359 --> 00:22:06,039
I know that to save your mom...

568
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,160
...you had no other choice.

569
00:22:07,759 --> 00:22:08,480
Hiding it from me...

570
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,880
...was because you didn't want to make me sad.

571
00:22:13,319 --> 00:22:15,519
But I've already decided.

572
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:18,079
No matter how long you have left to live...

573
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,680
...I will be with you.

574
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:30,039
Maybe I'll be sad or regret it in the future...

575
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:33,119
...but I'm willing to bear that future.

576
00:22:39,799 --> 00:22:40,400
Xu Rui.

577
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,440
Don't get emotional just yet.

578
00:22:43,839 --> 00:22:45,160
Have you thought about what to do later?

579
00:22:45,599 --> 00:22:46,240
What "later"?

580
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:48,119
You know...

581
00:22:49,079 --> 00:22:50,519
...if you really die.

582
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:54,720
If I kick the bucket, I kick the bucket.

583
00:22:54,839 --> 00:22:56,000
Live well while I'm alive.

584
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:57,000
Cherish the present.

585
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,559
And leave no regrets when I die.

586
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,359
I knew you'd say that.

587
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:02,000
And then?

588
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:04,480
Leave Auntie to us after she loses her son?

589
00:23:05,079 --> 00:23:07,039
Let me and Li Wai explain to Auntie...

590
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:08,400
...that to trade your life for hers...

591
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,480
...you left so early?

592
00:23:09,559 --> 00:23:10,359
You can't say that.

593
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:12,039
Kong Xiaocan, let me tell you.

594
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:14,319
You clean up your own mess.

595
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:15,519
Figure out what to do.

596
00:23:18,079 --> 00:23:18,720
Also...

597
00:23:20,279 --> 00:23:21,839
Don't go around with that head. It's so ugly.

598
00:23:22,759 --> 00:23:23,160
Xu Rui.

599
00:23:26,759 --> 00:23:27,680
You turn hostile so fast.

600
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:35,920
I don't think I ever thought about what comes after.

601
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:40,359
What will my mom do without me?

602
00:23:41,039 --> 00:23:41,720
Regret it now?

603
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:44,039
If I hadn't traded my lifespan back then...

604
00:23:44,039 --> 00:23:45,640
...couldn't I have grown old with Xu Rui?

605
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:47,279
But...

606
00:23:48,119 --> 00:23:50,319
...could I just watch my mom leave me?

607
00:23:54,839 --> 00:23:55,480
Xiaocan.

608
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:57,079
Xiaocan, look.

609
00:23:57,599 --> 00:23:59,160
Look at this selfie stick I just bought.

610
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:00,240
It only cost 38.8.

611
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,200
It's the upgraded version, too.

612
00:24:01,519 --> 00:24:02,519
It even has this little light.

613
00:24:02,799 --> 00:24:04,039
It makes people look really good.

614
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:04,799
Let me tell you...

615
00:24:04,799 --> 00:24:06,160
...let's take lots of photos this time.

616
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:07,480
We haven't gone out for fun in ages.

617
00:24:09,039 --> 00:24:10,279
Your hair...

618
00:24:12,519 --> 00:24:13,400
Anyway, it's better than this morning.

619
00:24:13,640 --> 00:24:14,799
Come on, let's take a picture.

620
00:24:21,079 --> 00:24:21,920
One, two...

621
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:22,920
If I'm gone...

622
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:25,079
...how could my mom possibly accept it?

623
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:33,480
You silly child

624
00:24:34,039 --> 00:24:35,319
What did I tell you?

625
00:24:36,759 --> 00:24:38,119
I told you to slack off a bit during training

626
00:24:38,519 --> 00:24:39,400
But you just had to work so hard

627
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:42,759
Luckily you didn't hurt the bone

628
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,960
Next time you train,

629
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:48,119
listen to Mom

630
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:50,279
You don't need to run so fast

631
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:55,000
Does it hurt?

632
00:24:55,519 --> 00:24:56,680
Did Mom press too hard?

633
00:25:02,839 --> 00:25:03,720
What's wrong?

634
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:07,000
What is it?

635
00:25:08,119 --> 00:25:09,720
Tell Mom what's on your mind

636
00:25:14,359 --> 00:25:15,039
Okay, don't say it, don't say it

637
00:25:15,599 --> 00:25:16,440
Don't cry. Don't cry

638
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:18,720
Stop crying. Stop crying

639
00:25:19,079 --> 00:25:19,519
Sweetheart

640
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,720
It's okay. Mom is here

641
00:25:27,279 --> 00:25:28,119
Hurry up, you two

642
00:25:31,559 --> 00:25:33,119
I really regret agreeing to go to Hainan

643
00:25:33,680 --> 00:25:35,240
Why aren't we taking a plane?

644
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:36,319
Shut up, you two

645
00:25:36,759 --> 00:25:38,359
Look how diligent our Agricultural College classmates are

646
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:40,359
Look at what time Xiao Tian gets up to memorize words

647
00:25:40,359 --> 00:25:42,119
And look at what time Xu Rui gets up to train

648
00:25:43,359 --> 00:25:44,680
Other people's kids are always better

649
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:46,599
Even my mom thinks you're much better than me

650
00:25:46,799 --> 00:25:47,920
Everyone's mom thinks that

651
00:25:50,279 --> 00:25:51,279
Fang'er! Over here! Here!

652
00:25:51,359 --> 00:25:51,839
Here! Here! Here!

653
00:25:51,839 --> 00:25:52,599
Come on! Come on! Come on!

654
00:25:52,599 --> 00:25:53,000
Coming

655
00:25:53,279 --> 00:25:53,640
Fangfang

656
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,759
Fang'er, sit, sit, sit. Sit here

657
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:56,720
Okay, put it down. Leave it. I'll get it, I'll get it

658
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,279
Come, come, come. Put it over here

659
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,480
What did you bring? My goodness

660
00:26:01,079 --> 00:26:01,799
Careful

661
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:03,200
Careful. Careful. Careful

662
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,440
Then the two of us will be in front

663
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:05,359
We're going ahead now

664
00:26:05,359 --> 00:26:06,240
Okay, okay, okay. Bye

665
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:07,200
You guys chat. You guys chat

666
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:07,759
See you later

667
00:26:08,359 --> 00:26:09,440
Bye-bye. Bye-bye. Bye-bye

668
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:10,640
Finally on board

669
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:12,039
Why are so many people going?

670
00:26:13,039 --> 00:26:14,480
They all say they don't want to go,

671
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:16,920
but actually, they're either afraid of missing grad school points,

672
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:18,119
or they want to pad their resumes

673
00:26:18,359 --> 00:26:19,000
You have no idea

674
00:26:19,359 --> 00:26:21,079
After you chased Professor Wang out that day,

675
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:22,799
everyone signed up so enthusiastically

676
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,440
Come, come. Sit here

677
00:26:24,559 --> 00:26:26,039
Have you had that Hainan chicken rice?

678
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:27,400
It's here

679
00:26:27,519 --> 00:26:28,200
Did... did it go well?

680
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:28,720
Is it tasty?

681
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:29,319
Sister Rui

682
00:26:29,599 --> 00:26:30,079
Brother Xiaocan

683
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:30,839
Brother Li Wai

684
00:26:37,039 --> 00:26:37,880
Let me check my bunk

685
00:26:39,599 --> 00:26:40,119
Cool

686
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:40,880
Cool, right?

687
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:41,279
Cool

688
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:42,960
Um, this spot is taken

689
00:26:43,079 --> 00:26:44,759
This is our bunk. Pass

690
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:46,039
Is the pork trotter rice from here?

691
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:46,920
No

692
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:47,759
Then it's from Guangdong

693
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:48,640
Come on

694
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:49,400
What's wrong?

695
00:26:49,839 --> 00:26:51,759
They're sitting on our bunks

696
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:53,960
Are you in the lower bunks?

697
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,880
It's a straight, can't help it

698
00:26:56,799 --> 00:26:57,759
Excuse me, excuse me

699
00:26:58,599 --> 00:27:00,359
Is your seat here on the lower bunk?

700
00:27:00,759 --> 00:27:01,880
We're just sitting for a bit

701
00:27:02,079 --> 00:27:02,880
Come on, hurry up

702
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:04,240
No, we're just playing cards...

703
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:06,720
This spot belongs to these young girls

704
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:08,920
I'll bomb you

705
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:09,799
Can I see your tickets?

706
00:27:09,799 --> 00:27:11,799
These two girls say this spot is theirs

707
00:27:12,839 --> 00:27:14,119
No, show me your ticket

708
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:15,799
Three with a pair

709
00:27:16,079 --> 00:27:16,920
These two girls...

710
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,079
...need to rest now

711
00:27:18,079 --> 00:27:19,519
You are occupying their seats

712
00:27:19,599 --> 00:27:19,960
Pass

713
00:27:21,519 --> 00:27:22,559
Did you hear what I said?

714
00:27:24,079 --> 00:27:24,880
If you keep this up...

715
00:27:24,880 --> 00:27:26,799
I'm going to get the conductor and the train police

716
00:27:27,319 --> 00:27:27,640
Pass

717
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:29,160
Stop playing, stop playing

718
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:30,359
You're sitting in their spots

719
00:27:30,359 --> 00:27:31,359
Did you get their permission?

720
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:32,480
Did you ask them?

721
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:33,759
They need to rest now

722
00:27:33,759 --> 00:27:34,640
Get out of here, now

723
00:27:35,319 --> 00:27:36,920
Where's your ticket? Hurry up, pack up

724
00:27:37,519 --> 00:27:39,359
Come on, let's go play cards over at my side

725
00:27:39,839 --> 00:27:40,480
What a killjoy

726
00:27:43,519 --> 00:27:44,680
Young girls these days...

727
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:46,240
You even got their bed dirty

728
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,079
Rest up, rest up

729
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,359
Thanks, Guifang

730
00:27:52,359 --> 00:27:52,960
Thanks

731
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,920
Guifang is really amazing

732
00:27:56,119 --> 00:27:58,400
Why am I starting to like her a little?

733
00:28:10,599 --> 00:28:11,440
Are you the only one here?

734
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:12,480
Take a corn to eat, hurry

735
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:13,279
Take it and eat

736
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:14,960
Okay, don't be shy

737
00:28:15,279 --> 00:28:16,920
Here, taste what we developed ourselves

738
00:28:17,039 --> 00:28:17,599
Take a bag with you

739
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:18,720
Professor Wang

740
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:23,200
Sit here, sit here

741
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:26,079
You cuties are here

742
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:28,519
Taste it, our self-developed products

743
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:29,400
Have a corn

744
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:37,359
I... I turned on the beauty filter

745
00:28:37,559 --> 00:28:38,799
Beauty filter is on, snap away

746
00:28:40,559 --> 00:28:41,519
Not taking photos anymore, never mind

747
00:28:43,839 --> 00:28:45,079
Why are you so uptight?

748
00:28:45,839 --> 00:28:47,240
Am I a tiger? Will I eat you?

749
00:28:48,759 --> 00:28:49,839
Am I usually that fierce?

750
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:50,599
No, no

751
00:28:50,599 --> 00:28:51,519
Am I fierce in class?

752
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,079
Professor Wang

753
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:55,920
This tomato is really delicious

754
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:56,720
What variety is it?

755
00:28:56,920 --> 00:28:57,519
Newly developed

756
00:28:57,519 --> 00:28:58,039
Good, right?

757
00:28:59,000 --> 00:28:59,599
That explains it

758
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:02,039
I feel like tomatoes these days have less and less flavor

759
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:02,839
This is really good

760
00:29:02,839 --> 00:29:03,759
This not only has flavor...

761
00:29:03,759 --> 00:29:05,400
...but is also easy to transport and store

762
00:29:05,559 --> 00:29:06,400
So more people...

763
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:07,640
...can taste our new variety

764
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,759
This is why we study agriculture

765
00:29:12,759 --> 00:29:13,559
There's a rehearsal today

766
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:14,680
I'll pick you up in a bit

767
00:29:29,039 --> 00:29:29,720
My head.

768
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,440
My intelligence and wisdom.

769
00:29:31,799 --> 00:29:32,480
All knocked out of me.

770
00:29:32,559 --> 00:29:33,400
Are you okay, Brother Li Wai?

771
00:29:33,799 --> 00:29:35,400
My god, this upper bunk is hard on the head.

772
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:36,559
My god, I can't even straighten my back.

773
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:38,400
Can't straighten my legs either.

774
00:29:39,279 --> 00:29:41,599
But do you know what this upper bunk is good for?

775
00:29:44,279 --> 00:29:45,960
Doing planks.

776
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:52,000
Godmother, what good stuff are you eating?

777
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:53,880
There's good food over there.

778
00:29:54,319 --> 00:29:54,640
Let's go.

779
00:29:55,599 --> 00:29:55,960
Let's go.

780
00:29:56,359 --> 00:29:58,319
I'll count one, two, three, see who climbs down faster.

781
00:29:58,559 --> 00:29:58,960
Okay.

782
00:29:59,559 --> 00:29:59,960
One.

783
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:01,000
Three.

784
00:30:10,119 --> 00:30:11,319
I can't find the foothold, wait a sec.

785
00:30:12,839 --> 00:30:13,640
This is too hard to get down from.

786
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,000
Sorry, brother.

787
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:20,440
Brother Xiaocan, Sister Xu Rui.

788
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,119
Why don't you join us...

789
00:30:22,119 --> 00:30:22,759
Tian, Tian, Tian.

790
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,240
Uh, let's go eat something good.

791
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:25,119
Let's not stay here and watch the PDA.

792
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:25,920
Let's go.

793
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:28,119
Godmother.

794
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,400
Godmother.

795
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:31,680
Before, I...

796
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:33,960
didn't feel it that much.

797
00:30:36,160 --> 00:30:37,759
But these past two days, I've been really scared.

798
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:39,960
Can't sleep at night.

799
00:30:41,599 --> 00:30:42,200
I was thinking,

800
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,880
if I really just suddenly disappeared,

801
00:30:47,359 --> 00:30:48,559
what would my mom do all alone?

802
00:30:54,039 --> 00:30:55,319
You're only scared now?

803
00:31:02,240 --> 00:31:02,880
Alright, alright.

804
00:31:03,039 --> 00:31:04,440
Go, chat with them.

805
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:05,559
Go.

806
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:10,240
You saw it.

807
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:11,680
Saw it this time.

808
00:31:12,279 --> 00:31:12,799
We...

809
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:13,440
No.

810
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:15,160
That must be someone sticking their head out.

811
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:15,920
Get me two oranges.

812
00:31:17,119 --> 00:31:17,440
Here.

813
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:17,880
Give me one.

814
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:18,359
Thanks, thanks.

815
00:31:20,119 --> 00:31:21,480
And that corn smells really good too.

816
00:31:22,079 --> 00:31:22,720
The size is a bit bigger.

817
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:23,039
Right?

818
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:52,200
This corn is a new variety too.

819
00:31:52,240 --> 00:31:53,759
Didn't you notice it's bigger than the others?

820
00:31:53,799 --> 00:31:54,119
Right?

821
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:55,839
Didn't you notice this corn...

822
00:31:55,839 --> 00:31:56,359
The orange dropped.

823
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:57,599
It's okay, I got it, I got it.

824
00:31:58,640 --> 00:31:59,480
Excuse me, sorry.

825
00:32:00,079 --> 00:32:00,799
Sorry, excuse me.

826
00:32:00,799 --> 00:32:01,200
Sorry.

827
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,000
The tomato is really delicious.

828
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:07,000
It looks good too.

829
00:32:11,319 --> 00:32:12,200
Taste this.

830
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,640
Seemed like something flashed by.

831
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:14,599
This is just an orange.

832
00:32:14,599 --> 00:32:15,039
Is it?

833
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,599
Try it, maybe I'm seeing things.

834
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:23,799
It is indeed quite tasty.

835
00:32:23,799 --> 00:32:24,240
Thanks.

836
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:25,200
This is my Coke.

837
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:27,960
Forget it, you drink it.

838
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:28,480
I don't want it anymore.

839
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:53,680
Husband.

840
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:55,799
Let's name our child Aotian.

841
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:17,200
Xiaocan.

842
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:19,400
Xiaocan.

843
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:20,680
Are you okay?

844
00:33:22,240 --> 00:33:22,799
Xiaocan.

845
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:24,200
Open the door, please.

846
00:33:24,759 --> 00:33:25,839
Open the door first.

847
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,160
Xiaocan.

848
00:33:27,559 --> 00:33:28,400
Open the door!

849
00:33:29,359 --> 00:33:29,880
